dataset.name: MIS Load Log

dataset.name: Current Establishment
dataset.query: dataset_base_ AS (SELECT AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.OFFENDER_ID_DISPLAY, AT_ESTABLISHMENT.ESTABLISHMENT_CODE_NK FROM BODIMIS.DIM_DATE AT_CASE_NOTE_CONTACT_DATE, BODIMIS.DIM_REFERENCE_CODES AT_CASE_NOTE_TYPE, BODIMIS.DIM_ESTABLISHMENT AT_ESTABLISHMENT, BODIMIS.DIM_OFFENDER_BOOKING AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING, BODIMIS.FACT_BED_ASSIGNMENT_HISTORY AT_BED_ASSIGNMENT_HISTORY, BODIMIS.DIM_ESTABLISHMENT MOVEMENT_TO_ESTABLISHMENT, BODIMIS.DIM_CELL AT_CELL, BODIMIS.FACT_OFFENDER_CASE_NOTE AT_FACT_OFFENDER_CASE_NOTE, BODIMIS.DIM_CELL AT_TO_CELL WHERE (AT_CELL.ESTABLISHMENT_SK = AT_ESTABLISHMENT.ESTABLISHMENT_SK) AND (AT_CELL.UNIT_4_SK = AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.LIVING_UNIT_SK) AND (AT_BED_ASSIGNMENT_HISTORY.OFFENDER_BOOKING_SK (+) = AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.OFFENDER_BOOKING_SK) AND (AT_BED_ASSIGNMENT_HISTORY.LIVING_UNIT_SK = AT_TO_CELL.UNIT_4_SK (+)) AND (AT_ESTABLISHMENT.ACTIVE_FLAG = 'Y') AND (AT_TO_CELL.ESTABLISHMENT_SK = MOVEMENT_TO_ESTABLISHMENT.ESTABLISHMENT_SK (+)) AND (AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.OFFENDER_BOOKING_SK IN (SELECT CSL.OFFENDER_BOOKING_SK FROM BODIMIS.DIM_STAFF_ACCESSIBLE_CASELOAD SAC, BODIMIS.DIM_CASELOAD_SECURITY_LIST CSL WHERE SAC.CASELOAD_ID = CSL.CASELOAD_CODE AND SAC.USERNAME = (SELECT username FROM context_) AND CSL.ENDYEAR >= TO_CHAR(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, 'YYYY') - 6)) AND (AT_CASE_NOTE_CONTACT_DATE.DATE_SK = AT_FACT_OFFENDER_CASE_NOTE.CONTACT_DATE_SK) AND (AT_CASE_NOTE_TYPE.REFERENCE_CODE_SK = AT_FACT_OFFENDER_CASE_NOTE.CASE_NOTE_TYPE_CODE_SK) AND (AT_CASE_NOTE_TYPE.CODE_DOMAIN = 'TASK_TYPE') AND (AT_FACT_OFFENDER_CASE_NOTE.OFFENDER_BOOKING_SK (+) = AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.OFFENDER_BOOKING_SK) AND (((TRUNC((AT_BED_ASSIGNMENT_HISTORY.ASSIGNMENT_TIME)) <= TO_DATE('01-02-2018 00:00:00', 'DD-MM-YYYY HH24:MI:SS') AND AT_BED_ASSIGNMENT_HISTORY.ASSIGNMENT_END_TIME IS NULL) OR (TRUNC((AT_BED_ASSIGNMENT_HISTORY.ASSIGNMENT_TIME)) <= TO_DATE('01-02-2018 00:00:00', 'DD-MM-YYYY HH24:MI:SS') AND AT_BED_ASSIGNMENT_HISTORY.ASSIGNMENT_END_TIME >= TO_DATE('01-12-2017 00:00:00', 'DD-MM-YYYY HH24:MI:SS'))) AND AT_BED_ASSIGNMENT_HISTORY.ASSIGNMENT_TIME <= AT_CASE_NOTE_CONTACT_DATE.DAY_DATE AND AT_BED_ASSIGNMENT_HISTORY.ASSIGNMENT_END_TIME >= AT_CASE_NOTE_CONTACT_DATE.DAY_DATE AND MOVEMENT_TO_ESTABLISHMENT.ESTABLISHMENT_CODE_NK = (SELECT establishment_code FROM prompt_) AND AT_CASE_NOTE_TYPE.CODE = 'KA')), dataset_ AS (SELECT OFFENDER_ID_DISPLAY, ESTABLISHMENT_CODE_NK FROM dataset_base_)
